                                          <h1 class="nodeTitle">
                David Limbaugh: Media Prefer Hating Trump to Helping America
              </h1>
                            <div class="nodeInfo">
                <div id="nodeAuthorInfo">
                                      <a href="/user/1104"><img class="authorImg image-style-node-author-image img-fluid" src="https://cdn.cnsnews.com/styles/node_author_image/s3/pictures/picture-1104-1510326653.png?itok=q_y8Kn9c" width="50" height="50" alt="" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</a>
                                      

                  By <a id="CBAuthor" href="/user/1104">David Limbaugh</a>

                  
                  | April 17, 2020 | 10:35am EDT
                  
                </div>  

              </div>
              <div class="nodeButtons">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
